  <front>
    <title>Uniform Resource Name (URN) Namespace Definitions</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-ietf-urnbis-rfc3406bis-urn-ns-reg-04"/>
    <author initials="P." surname="Saint-Andre" fullname="Peter Saint-Andre"/>
    <author initials="L." surname="Daigle" fullname="Leslie Daigle"/>
    <author initials="R." surname="Iannella" fullname="Renato Iannella"/>
    <date day="27" month="November" year="2012"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document supplements the Uniform Resource Name (URN) syntax
   specification by defining the concept of a URN namespace, as well as
   mechanisms for defining and registering such namespaces.  This
   document obsoletes RFC 3406.</t>
